<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Seller Account Rejected</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 24px; }
    .reason-box { background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; margin: 16px 0; color: #991b1b; }
    .footer { color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin:0">Seller Application Update</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <strong>{{sellerName}}</strong>,</p>
    <p>We have reviewed your seller application for <strong>{{shopName}}</strong> and unfortunately it has not been approved at this time.</p>

    {{#if rejectedReason}}
    <p><strong>Reason:</strong></p>
    <div class="reason-box">{{rejectedReason}}</div>
    {{/if}}

    <p>If you believe this is a mistake or would like to re-apply after addressing the issues, please contact our support team.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact support.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
